The paper proposes a new approach to archetypal analysis using neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with data transformation and feature extraction, which are common topics in signal processing and information theory (cs.SI). The use of neural networks for transformation and identification of archetypal states is also related to the field of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with data analysis and pattern recognition, which are topics in data science (cs.DS).
